  "prompt": "Which is the best cream available in india with Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, Ester C and Dermaxyl?",
  "response": "There are several creams available in India that combine **Kojic Acid**, **Alpha Arbutin**, **Ester C**, and **Dermaxyl** for skin brightening, pigmentation reduction, and anti-aging benefits. Below are some of the best options:\n\n---\n\n### **1. **Dermafique Skin Radiance Cream****\n- **Key Ingredients**: Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, Ester C, and Dermaxyl.\n- **Benefits**: Reduces dark spots, evens skin tone, improves radiance, and boosts collagen.\n- **Why It\u2019s Great**: Dermatologist-recommended, lightweight, and non-greasy formulation.\n\n---\n\n### **2. **Kaya Pigmentation Reducing Complex****\n- **Key Ingredients**: Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, and Ester C.\n- **Benefits**: Targets hyperpigmentation, brightens skin, and reduces dark spots.\n- **Why It\u2019s Great**: Clinically tested and suitable for all skin types.\n\n---\n\n### **3. **La Piel Brightening Cream****\n- **Key Ingredients**: Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, and Ester C.\n- **Benefits**: Fades discoloration, improves skin texture, and provides antioxidant protection.\n- **Why It\u2019s Great**: Paraben-free and formulated for Indian skin.\n\n---\n\n### **4. **Brihat Whitening Cream****\n- **Key Ingredients**: Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, and Dermaxyl.\n- **Benefits**: Reduces pigmentation, brightens skin, and enhances elasticity.\n- **Why It\u2019s Great**: Affordable and effective for long-term use.\n\n---\n\n### **5. **Lotus Professional Phyto RX Whitening and Brightening Cream****\n- **Key Ingredients**: Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, and Ester C.\n- **Benefits**: Lightens dark spots, evens skin tone, and protects against oxidative stress.\n- **Why It\u2019s Great**: Salon-grade product with visible results in weeks.\n\n---\n\n### **6. **Vyas Vita White Cream****\n- **Key Ingredients**: Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, and Ester C.\n- **Benefits**: Reduces pigmentation, prevents tanning, and improves skin clarity.\n- **Why It\u2019s Great**: Ayurvedic formulation with modern actives.\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Cream**:\n1. **Skin Type**: Choose a product suited for your skin type (oily, dry, combination, or sensitive).\n2. **Patch Test**: Always perform a patch test to avoid allergic reactions.\n3. **Consistency**: Use the cream consistently for at least 4-6 weeks to see visible results.\n4. **SPF**: Pair with a good sunscreen (SPF 30 or higher) during the day to protect your skin from UV rays.\n\n---\n\nIf you\u2019re looking for a cream with **all four ingredients** (Kojic Acid, Alpha Arbutin, Ester C, and Dermaxyl), **Dermafique Skin Radiance Cream** is one of the best options available in India. Always consult a dermatologist before starting any new skincare product.",
